{"lastModified":1761659023060,"uri":"c::25855039017::vessel::c0bed5a0-f9ba-11ef-9ffc-1177459b1fa8","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Naples, Procida, Ischia, Capri, Positano, Sorrento, Amali Coast, Ponza, Ventotene\n\nThe Azimut Magellano 53 stands as an ideal yacht for extended cruises, providing a guarantee of smooth sailing across diverse marine conditions.\n\nIts distinctive Dual Mode hull ensures both comfort and excellent seakeeping, even in \nmild sea conditions.\n\nThe interior spaces are thoughtfully designed for extended stays on board, featuring welcoming living areas and spacious cabins.\n\nThe cockpit serves as a terrace overlooking the sea, allowing you to bask in the spectacle \noffered by nature. The exclusive dining room provides a captivating backdrop for picturesque \nsunset aperitifs and delightful breakfasts.\n\nThe yacht is well-appointed with a master bedroom, a VIP bedroom, and a bunk bed, ensuring a luxurious and comfortable onboard experience.\n\n\nThe expansive windows in the  living room provide a panoramic 360° view of the sea, infusing brightness into every corner.\n\nNoble materials, exquisite fabrics, and refined finishes characterize each aspect, showcasing Azimut Yachts' meticulous Italian craftsmanship and the intricate attention invested in every detail.\n\nThe versatile space ensures maximum comfort for all guests, promising a luxurious experience tailored to meet every need.\n\nRECOMMENDED FLOW \n8/10 people for 1 day excursion \n4/6 people per stay with overnight stay on board\n\nINCLUDED IN THE PRICE:\nSkipper, hostess, welcome on board prosecco, snacks & soft drinks, beach towels, snorkeling equipment, sup.","blueprint":{"name":"MAGELLANO 53","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::c0bed5a0-f9ba-11ef-9ffc-1177459b1fa8::assets::0a1b19c0-f9c0-11ef-b138-059909f1dda7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c0bed5a0-f9ba-11ef-9ffc-1177459b1fa8::assets::0a1e2700-f9c0-11ef-b13a-059909f1dda7/{imageVaria